Title: Logitech G512 Mechanical Gaming Keyboard
Desc: G512 is a high-performance gaming keyboard featuring your choice of advanced Romer-G Tactile. Romer-G Linear and GX Blue mechanical switches. Advanced gaming technology and aluminum-alloy construction make G512 simple. durable and full-featured.

Title: Logitech G613 Wireless Mechanical Gaming Keyboard
Desc: G613 is a next generation wireless keyboard designed for gamers who demand both the high performance capabilities of mechanical switches and the freedom of wireless gaming.

Title: Logitech G910 RGB Mechanical Gaming Keyboard
Desc: The highest levels performance. engineering. and design. G910 is fully loaded with programmable G-keys. LIGHTSYNC RGB. Romer-G Tactile switches. integrated palmrest and more.

Title: Logitech G213 RGB Gaming Keyboard
Desc: The G213 gaming keyboard features Logitech G Mech-Dome keys that are specially tuned to deliver a superior tactile response and overall performance profile similar to a mechanical keyboard. Mech-Dome keys are full height. deliver a full 4mm travel distance. 50g actuation force. and a quiet sound operation.
